<section class="mushroom-benefits">
  {%- comment -%} Rolling water layers, shared component with the product pages {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="wave-field" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="wave wave--back"></span>
    <span class="wave wave--mid"></span>
    <span class="wave wave--front"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Why It Works</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Awaken Your Mind.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">2,000mg of dual-extracted functional mushrooms and deep ocean minerals in every can — caffeine-free, so it works at 8am, at the gym, or instead of a beer.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits-grid">

      <!-- Think Sharp -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon-wrap">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6260AE" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M9.5 2.5C7 2.5 5 4.5 5 7c0 1.8.9 3.3 2.3 4.2A3 3 0 0 0 6 13.5a3 3 0 0 0 2.1 2.87C8.4 17.9 9.6 19 11 19h2c1.4 0 2.6-1.1 2.9-2.63A3 3 0 0 0 18 13.5a3 3 0 0 0-1.3-2.48A4.5 4.5 0 0 0 14.5 2.5c-.9 0-1.7.28-2.3.75a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-2.7-.75z"/>
            <path d="M12 10v6M9.5 13h5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Think Sharp</h3>
        <div class="benefit-dose">900mg Lion's Mane</div>
        <p>The clarity mushroom, dual-extracted from 100% fruiting bodies. For the 2pm wall, the deadline sprint, the long drive home.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Natural Lift -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon-wrap">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6260AE" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M13 2L4.5 13.5H11L10 22l9.5-11.5H13L13 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Natural Lift</h3>
        <div class="benefit-dose">700mg Cordyceps</div>
        <p>An athlete's favorite. Supports your body's own energy production, so the lift builds instead of spiking. Perfect before the gym.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stay Steady -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon-wrap">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6260AE" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22V12"/>
            <path d="M12 12C12 12 7 10 6 6c3 0 6 2 6 6z"/>
            <path d="M12 12c0 0 5-2 6-6-3 0-6 2-6 6z"/>
            <path d="M12 12c0 0-3-5-1-9 2 1 4 5 1 9z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Stay Steady</h3>
        <div class="benefit-dose">400mg Reishi</div>
        <p>The adaptogen that keeps the lift smooth. Balanced and even, never wired — which is why this one works after work, not just before it.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Deep Hydration -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon-wrap">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6260AE" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 3C12 3 5 10.5 5 15a7 7 0 0 0 14 0c0-4.5-7-12-7-12z"/>
            <path d="M9.5 16.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 3.5 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Deep Hydration</h3>
        <div class="benefit-dose">Ocean Minerals</div>
        <p>Magnesium and calcium drawn from deep seawater. Replaces what you actually lose, so you rehydrate — not just drink.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
    <p class="benefits-disclaimer">† These statements have not been evaluated by the FDA. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.</p>
  </div>
</section>

